## Authority Model

- `Docs/Architecture/*` is current truth.
- `Docs/Proposals/*` holds design-in-progress when that subtree is present.
- `Docs/Decisions/*`, `Docs/Migrations/*`, and `Docs/Archive/*` hold history
  when those subtrees are present.
- `.github/*` holds GitHub-facing governance.
- Root governance files such as `CONTRIBUTING.md` hold repo-wide contributor
  guidance.
